title: DJ Led Manville - Versus Satanicus II (2007)
description:
DJ Led Manville - Versus Satanicus II (2007)

Hi. I&#039;m Led Manville. One of my passions is music, doing it and djing it too. The bands i mix are mainly ebm, futurepop, industrial, synth, electro, trance, psy and gothic. I do harmonic mixing, so appart from beatmatching i try to fit also the melodies from one song to another. I&#039;ve been djing since 20 years ago in many clubs and parties in Madrid.

Dj Led Manville presents: Versus Satanicus II

"Each song is the result of mixing 2 songs playing from their
begining to their end.
No song was altered previously.
All necessary adjustments were done during live mixing.
No song was injured during the recording of this album ;)"

Encoder...: Lame 3.97
Quality...: VBR kbps / 44,1Hz / Joint-Stereo

Enjoy this new release :)

Keep it black, keep the scene alive!
